data.description: "QUALIFYING ASSUMABLE (30yr Amortization) FHA LOAN 2.875% FIXED RATE Balance of $213k, (Per the Seller)" New Roof and new windows installed 2023. This MOVE-IN Ready home has all of the desired features! Open, Living Area Concept with vaulted ceilings and the popular split-bedroom design. The kitchen is equipped with attractive stainless steel appliances and the island/breakfast bar offers the perfect workspace as well as additional seating. The home interior is a comfortable neutral palette, as well as the tile floors that flow throughout the home with the exception of the bedroom that has warm hue, wood-like flooring. The screened-in Lanai, accessible off the kitchen, is spacious for relaxing or entertaining while overlooking the large backyard. Large utility room. 2 car attached garage. Great location to nearby shopping, dining, sports and US 41. Call to schedule your home tour today.
